msgid "若需上传大文件（超过 10MB），建议将 <code>upload_max_filesize</code> 和 <code>post_max_size</code> 调至至少 64M。"
msgstr "To upload large files (>10MB), set <code>upload_max_filesize</code> and <code>post_max_size</code> to at least 64M."

msgid "🛠️ SBA 防御设置"
msgstr "🛠️ SBA Defense Settings"

msgid "📖 使用说明"
msgstr "📖 Instructions"

msgid "1. <b>防误杀：</b> 填入用户名后，登录时将免疫所有频率拦截和路径检测。"
msgstr "1. <b>Whitelist:</b> Whitelisted users are immune to rate limits and path detection."

msgid "2. <b>Gate 钥匙：</b> 设置后，访问 <code>wp-login.php?gate=钥匙</code> 可开启登录入口（地址栏自动去除参数）。此后登录表单通过隐藏字段提交令牌，退出后令牌失效。"
msgstr "2. <b>Gate Key:</b> Protect login via <code>wp-login.php?gate=KEY</code>. The parameter is hidden after access."

msgid "3. <b>指纹库：</b> 自动识别 <code>sqlmap, curl, wget, python</code> 等 UA 特征并阻断。"
msgstr "3. <b>Fingerprinting:</b> Automatically blocks UA like <code>sqlmap, curl, wget, python</code>."

msgid "4. <b>归属地：</b> 使用 ip2region xdb 内存查询。请通过下方按钮上传 IPv4 和 IPv6 的 xdb 文件（支持分片上传、断点续传）。"
msgstr "4. <b>Geolocation:</b> Uses ip2region xdb. Upload IPv4/IPv6 files below (supports chunked upload)."

msgid "5. <b>爬虫防御：</b> 启用阶梯限制和 Cookie 校验可有效识别采集器，蜜罐陷阱触发即封禁。"
msgstr "5. <b>Crawler Defense:</b> Tiered limits and Cookie validation identify bots."

msgid "✅ 信任通道"
msgstr "✅ Trusted Channels"

msgid "用户名白名单"
msgstr "User Whitelist"

msgid "登录此用户时，系统自动信任，不执行拦截逻辑。"
msgstr "System automatically trusts this user; no blocking logic executed."

msgid "IP 白名单"
