msgid "启用强制 IP 直连 + Host 头校验"
msgstr "Enable Forced IP Connection + Host Header Validation"

msgid "防止攻击者利用短 TTL DNS 绕过 IP 黑名单。"
msgstr "Prevents attackers using short TTL DNS to bypass IP blacklists."

